
How to install
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

To install, please edit the file "install_vss.csh"

edit the first three directories (vmd plugin directory, tcl include file direcotry, tcl library directory) according to your system, e.g.

set VMDPLUGINDIR = ~/work/binary/vmd_plugins
set TCLINCDIR = /usr/include/tcl8.5
set TCLLIBDIR = /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu
 
then, type

./install_vss.csh


This will install vss to your current vmd plugin direcotry (VMDPLUGINDIR).

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


Tutorial
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

A tutorial on how to use vss is provided. 
See VSS_tutorial.pdf under the tutorial directory.
A short example is also given.

